      Maecenas ultricies mi eget mauris pharetra et. Neque gravida in fermentum et sollicitudin. Urna et pharetra pharetra massa massa ultricies mi quis. Viverra ipsum nunc aliquet bibendum enim facilisis. Sagittis eu volutpat odio facilisis mauris sit.
    </p>
    <div class="column col-12 full-width">
      <form id="get-started" method="post">
        <%= hidden_field_tag :authenticity_token, form_authenticity_token %>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label class="form-label" for="homepage_name">Name</label>
          <input class="form-input input-height" type="text" name="homepage[name]" id="homepage_name">

          <label class="form-label" for="email">Email</label>
          <input class="form-input input-height" type="email" name="homepage[email]" id="homepage_email">

          <div class="columns col-oneline">
            <div class="column col-6 pr-1">
              <label class="form-label" for="city">City</label>
              <input class="form-input input-height" type="text" name="homepage[city]" id="homepage_city">
            </div>
            <div class="column col-6 pl-1">
              <label class="form-label" for="state">State / Province / Region</label>
              <input class="form-input input-height" type="text"  name="homepage[state]" id="homepage_state" >
            </div>
          </div>

          <a id="contact-us"></a>

          <label class="form-label" for="country">Country</label>
          <input class="form-input input-height" type="text" name="homepage[country]" id="homepage_country">

          <label class="form-label" for="description">Which best describes you?</label>
          <select class="form-select input-height" name="homepage[description]" id="homepage_description" required>
            <option disabled selected value>Select one</option>
            <option>I’m starting or planning to open a lending library</option>
            <option>I manage or volunteer with an established lending library</option>
            <option>I’m just interested in learning more about Circulate</option>
          </select>

          <label class="form-label" for="inventory">Items in your inventory (optional)</label>
          <textarea class="form-input" name="homepage[inventory]"id="homepage_inventory" placeholder="If you are a part of an existing lending organization, what kinds of items are in your inventory?" rows="4"></textarea>

          <button class="btn input-group-btn mt-md" type="submit" form="get-started">Send</button>
        </div>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

